  <summary>The serial port monitor</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Easy to use</li>>
        <li>Customizable colours</li>
        <li>Remembers the last used settings</li>
        <li>Automatically reconnects to the serial port if the connection is lost</li>
        <li>Can log data to a file</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Depending on your system you may need to add a user to dialout group to open serial ports:
      <code>
        sudo usermod -a -G dialout $USER
      </code>>
    </p>
  </description>
